      "title": "Parliament is limited to 13 minutes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After Vetradhari Narendra Fernando placed the mace, the Parliament met under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena and after presenting the President's resignation letter as well as the resignation letter to the House, the Speaker announced that the Parliament would be adjourned until the 19th."
